Class DielsAlderStereo

    class DielsAlderStereo
extends Object
implements SearchConstants, StereoConstants
    Sets the stereochemistry of the product of a Diels-Alder reaction.

    • Field Detail

      • d_a_Product

        private final transient Molecule d_a_Product
        The calculated Diels-Alder product. Atoms derived from the diene are mapped 1-4; those from the dienophile are mapped 5-6; atom 1 is attached to 6, and 4 to 5; the out ligands of the diene termini are mapped 7 and 9; and the dienophile is mapped (11)(12)5=6(13)(14), with 11 cis to 13, and 12 cis to 14.

      • d_a_SMs
